panels.name: Top 10 IPs by Data Ingress
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=test/netflow
| json field=_raw"out_bytes","ipv4_dst_addr"
| count by ipv4_dst_addr, out_bytes
| sort by out_bytes
| limit 10
| fields - _count

panels.name: Top 10 Destination Ports
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=test/netflow
| json field=_raw "l4_dst_port" as dst_port
| count by dst_port
| top 10 dst_port by _count

panels.name: Top 10 Destination IPs
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=test/netflow
| json field=_raw "ipv4_dst_addr" as dst_ip
| count by dst_ip
| sort by _count
| limit 10

panels.name: Flow Record Outliers by Total Bytes per Minute
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=test/netflow 
| json field=_raw "in_bytes"
| json field=_raw "out_bytes"
| timeslice 1m
| in_bytes + out_bytes as total_bytes
| count _timeslice
//| transpose row _timeslice column total_bytes
| outlier _count window=5,threshold=3,consecutive=2,direction=+

panels.name: Flow Records per Protocol per Minute
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=test/netflow
| json field=_raw "protocol"
| timeslice 1m
| lookup Keyword from https://s3.amazonaws.com/sumologic-app-data/protocol-numbers.csv on protocol=Decimal
| count Keyword, _timeslice
| transpose row _timeslice column Keyword

panels.name: Top 10 IPs by Data Egress
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=test/netflow
| json field=_raw"out_bytes","ipv4_src_addr"
| count by ipv4_src_addr, out_bytes
| sort by out_bytes
| limit 10
| fields - _count

panels.name: Requests by Protocol
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=test/netflow
| json field=_raw "protocol"
| lookup Keyword from https://s3.amazonaws.com/sumologic-app-data/protocol-numbers.csv on protocol=Decimal
| count by Keyword
| top 10 Keyword by _count

panels.name: Top 10 Source IPs
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=test/netflow
| json field=_raw "ipv4_src_addr" as src_ip
| count by src_ip
| sort by _count
| limit 10
